error[S17]: A `version` `number` must have three dot-separated numeric components, with an optional pre-release/build suffix.
  --> dict.yaml:4:11
   |
LL | version:
LL |   number: "1.2.0.0"
   |           ^^^^^^^ `1.2.0.0` is not a valid version number
